image_number.description: An unique identifier for each page where the electronic or paper filing is reported.

11 C.F.R. § 102.15.
3. Enter into pre-probable cause conciliation with Michael David Pitts prior to a finding of probable cause to believe.

dated March 6, 2017.
5. Approve the Factual and Legal Analysis for Michael David Pitts, as recommended in the First General Counsel’s
Report dated March 6, 2017.
